>Ancient&Medieval/Fantasy
Anthros and humans exist in their own communities and civilizations, though some of them share the same towns and cities. Anthros are seen from noble savages, to barbarians, to overdeveloped beasts, to the freak experiment of some maddened wizard (sometimes true) by most humans, and are constantly fought, raided and enslaved by the commonly more civilized and developed human nations.
Anthros can fight back using their natural talents, but will often lose against human powers.
